      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The workflow for running MS2Query first uses MS2Deepscore to calculate spectral similarity scores between all library spectra and a query spectrum... By using pre-computed MS2Deepscore embeddings for library spectra, this full-library comparison can be computed much faster than existing alternatives... Next, the top 2000 spectra with the highest MS2Deepscore are selected.",
