      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Here we present MS2Query, a machine learning-based tool that integrates mass spectral embedding-based chemical similarity predictors (Spec2Vec and MS2Deepscore) as well as detected precursor masses to rank potential analogues and exact matches.",
