      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The intensities of the mass fragmentation peaks are normalised. Peaks above 1000 Da were removed and peaks with an intensity of less than 0,1 % of the highest peak were removed... Spectra with less than 3 peaks were completely removed from the library.",
