      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "MS2Query is available as an easily installable python package, which is stable and well-tested. The model as well as the library mass spectra used are available on Zenodo. MS2Query is fully automatic and was designed with the end-user in mind. For example, it outputs a CSV file with all relevant information about the found matches for the query spectra.",
