      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "To reduce the toll on working memory, this information is stored in a SQLite library. The precursor m/z is stored in a separate SQLite library column for efficient look-up speeds... This top 10 list of most related InChIKeys is pre-calculated for every unique InChIKey in the library and stored in the SQLite library.",
