      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "In the case of case studies 1-3 the spectra were uploaded on GNPS to run MSCluster to create consensus spectra... The data files for case study 4 were first converted to mzML format using Proteowizard... Next, LC-MS features were picked using XCMS3.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper uses MSCluster and XCMS3 for spectrum clustering and feature picking, not MZMine. MZMine is not mentioned in the paper. The card claims MZMine is used for preprocessing before MS2Query, but the paper uses alternative tools (MSCluster, XCMS3, Proteowizard).",
