      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "MS2Query is a tool for rapid large-scale MS2 library matching that enables searching both for analogues and exact matches in one run. MS2Query can reliably predict good analogues as well as exact library matches.",
