      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper is about MS2Query, a machine learning tool for mass spectral analogue search in metabolomics. It does not discuss Git workflows, feature branching, pull requests, or version control practices. The paper focuses on the scientific methodology and benchmarking of the tool, not software development practices.",
